description: Perhaps the most iconic freighter in the early Testudo line, the Mesa is essentially eight big boxes and a long corridor. The initial production run began in 2041 but lasted well into the late 2050s. While not produced in the same volume as the Edelweiss due to issues with assembly facilities, the Mesa is widely regarded as the first true freighter of the colony rush.
